<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <meta http-equiv="cleartype" content="on" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
    <meta name="description" content="" />
    <link type="text/plain" rel="author" href="/humans.txt" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon-32x32.png" sizes="32x32" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon-16x16.png" sizes="16x16" />

    <title>magmo</title>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application" %>
    <%= yield_content :stylesheets %>

    <% if content_for? :styles %>
      <style type="text/css">
        <%= yield_content :styles %>
      </style>
    <% end %>

    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300italic,400italic,600italic,700italic,800italic,400,300,600,700,800' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Merriweather:400,300,300italic,400italic,700,700italic,900,900italic' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

    <%= yield_content :head %>
  </head>

  <body id="page-top">

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light fixed-top" id="mainNav">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand js-scroll-trigger" href="#page-top">
            <%= image_tag 'logo+name-orange.svg', alt: 'Magmo' %>
        </a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler navbar-toggler-right" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarResponsive" aria-controls="navbarResponsive" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarResponsive">
          <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger" href="#about">About</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link" href="./force-move-games.pdf">Paper</a>
            </li>
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger" href="#contact">Contact</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="masthead text-center d-flex">
      <div class="container my-auto">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-uppercase">
              <strong>We build state channels</strong>
            </h1>
            <hr>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <p class="text-faded mb-5">
            ü¶Ñ To help ethereum scale! ü¶Ñ
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-xl js-scroll-trigger" href="#about">Find Out More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="bg-primary" id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Wait, what?</h2>
            <hr class="light my-4">
            <p class="text-faded mb-4">
              We are a team of researchers working on state channels - the most promising scaling 
              solution for the ethereum blockchain.
            </p>
            <p class="text faded mb-4">
            The technology exists today to allow a whole class of applications to move the majority of their transactions ‚Äúoff chain‚Äù. The complexity of understanding and applying state channel techniques is the main barrier to adoption.
            At Magmo, we‚Äôre working to make state channels more accessible to the Ethereum developer community.
            We are fortunate to be supported in this effort by the Ethereum Foundation and the Ethereum Community Fund.
            </p>

            <p class="text-faded mb-4">
            Our focus on simplicity and usability led us to develop ForceMove - a simple but powerful state channel framework, suitable for general use. 
            For more details read the <a href="./force-move-games.pdf">paper</a> or
            check out the <a href="https://github.com/magmo/force-move-games">code</a>!
            </p>

            <p class="text-faded mb-4">
             Our recently launched <a href="https://demo.magmo.com">Rock-Paper-Scissors game</a> is the first ForceMove application. The application is fully <a href="https://github.com/magmo/rps-poc">open-source</a> and designed to be used as a starting point for developers wanting to integrate state channels into their products.
            </p>



          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="section-heading">Let's Get In Touch!</h2>
            <hr class="my-4">
            <p class="mb-5">
              If you want to find out more about what we're doing or are interested in
              getting involved, please let us know!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-3 mr-auto text-center">
            <a href="https://github.com/magmo">
              <i class="fab fa-github fa-6x"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 mr-auto text-center">
            <a href="https://medium.com/magmo">
              <i class="fab fa-medium fa-6x"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 mr-auto text-center">
            <a href="https://twitter.com/magmoHQ">
              <i class="fab fa-twitter fa-6x"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 mr-auto text-center">
            <a href="mailto:research@magmo.com">
              <i class="far fa-envelope fa-6x"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Javascript -->
    <script defer src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.2/js/all.js"></script>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'modernizr-3.5.0.min' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application' %>
    <%= yield_content :javascripts %>
    <%= google_analytics_tag %>
  </body>
</html>
